WE HAVE CREATED THE REGISTRATION LOGIC INSIDE THE USERCONTROLLES 

WE ADDED BOT IF THE USER ACCOUNT EXISTS AND IF NOT WE WILL CREATE THE NEW USER ACCOUNT

WE HAVE THE LOGIN DETAILS INSIDE THE USER CONTROLLER
WE ARE USING BCRYPT TO HASH THE PASSWORD AND COMPARE THE PASSWORDS

WE ARE USING JWT TO GENERATE THE TOKENS AND SEND IT TO THE FRONT END

WE ARE USING MONGOOSE TO CONNECT TO THE MONGODB DATABASE

WE ARE USING EXPRESS TO CREATE THE ROUTES

WE ARE USING CORS TO ALLOW CROSS ORIGIN REQUESTS

WE ARE USING BODY PARSER TO PARSE THE REQUEST BODY